{"tid":374071,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"追到前後好大分別？！","createTime":"2017-08-25T13:08:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-25T15:35:54.000Z","uid":139749,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"49ada2ff291f0a645abae7421ce3cdbf868d4949","tid":374071,"uid":139749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:08:03.000Z","msg":"事程發展一個月都無<br />\n係咪都算多啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一開始未溝到就秒覆 得閒會打電話黎 <br />\n反工前打 lunchtime會打 收工又打 夜晚又傾<br />\n一開頭拍拖都ok既但過多幾日就變左<br />\n180度大變<br />\n成日失蹤 唔應機 <br />\n好想chur佢但又唔敢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n 過左幾日我頂唔順話不如做反朋友再算啦<br />\n佢撚都無撚就話好啦 <br />\n但有次岀街佢都照拖我手 又錫我<br />\n之後我問究竟係咩關係 <br />\n佢話係曖昧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我心諗曖昧係咁架咩<br />\n佢所謂既曖昧咪又係得閒就搵我<br />\n打風日個<br />\n佢好好死咁陪我<br />\n我以為係真心既<br />\n都係真心既 不過係真心蝦呃條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後 琴日有frd見到佢同佢所謂既EX岀街<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好想再信佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n請各位巴絲屌醒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4244e4e995cc2ebc0c057bf77bd9de627abc9e0","tid":374071,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:09:22.000Z","msg":"屌左?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffc77b31ac7ba3ca14a255eea1d051226aef249e","tid":374071,"uid":139749,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:14:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌左?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61d3497c8d2276d68518701c39e157cd6df5cea2","tid":374